{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_03_01",
  "title": "miho 1話  もうひとりの優勝者",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（NEXT VENUSグランプリ、歴代の優勝者を）\n（一堂に集めて祭典が行われることになった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The Next Venus Grand Prix‚ gathering all the past champions.）\n（It's become a festival where they all come together.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（星見プロからは、月ストとサニピが出演する）\n（……そして、うちの優勝経験者といえばもう一人……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（From Hoshimi Pro‚ Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace will perform.）\n（And… there's another former winner from our agency…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5666666348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "お断りします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll decline.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4999994595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、話くらい最後まで聞いて下さいよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ please listen to the end of the story…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.2666673978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんもスリクスを結成する前に……\nSundanceとしてグランプリで優勝してますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before forming IIIX‚ miho-san…\nYou won the Grand Prix as Sundance‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3666673978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……私の前のグループをご存じだったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So you knew about my previous group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9000020027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ知ってますよ。俺はマネージャーですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I knew it. I'm the manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3333362262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（Sundanceは、藤代葉さんとの二人組で）\n（BIG4にも迫ろうかという人気ユニットだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sundance‚ a duo with Fujishiro You before IIIX‚）\n（they were a popular unit approaching the BIG4.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.633338515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（しかし人気絶頂期に活動休止）\n（その後、mihoさんはⅢXを結成したわけだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But they went on hiatus at the height of their popularity.）\n（After that‚ miho-san formed IIIX…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4000036557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……昔のことですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's all in the past.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9666693051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "どうでしょう、先方もmihoさんに\nぜひ出てほしいとおっしゃってますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think? They really want miho-san\nto participate‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.6000036556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "お断りします\n今、スリクスは新曲リリースの準備で忙しいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll decline.\nRight now‚ IIIX is busy preparing for a new song release.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6666749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "ライブでのお披露目に、MVの撮影も控えてますし\nそこに余計な仕事を入れる余裕はありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have live performances to prepare for‚ and MV shoots coming up.\nThere's no room for extra work in our schedule.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1000082333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "貴方もマネージャーでしょう\n担当アイドルの仕事の予定をご存じのはずですが？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're a manager too‚ aren't you?\nYou should know your idol's schedule‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5333405494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……それに、Sundanceを知っているなら\nあのグループはもう終わったこともご存じのはず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…And if you know about Sundance‚\nyou should also know that group is long gone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9333395321,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9099.996344299996,
          "startTime": 88.0333358764
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "話はそれだけですか？\n……では、私はこれで失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that all you wanted to say?\n…Then‚ I'll excuse myself now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8333385149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（mihoさんの言うことはもっともだけど）\n（でも、せっかくの機会なのに、もったいないよな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（What miho-san says makes sense‚）\n（but it's a shame to miss such an opportunity…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8333374976,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5233.3292643999985,
          "startTime": 98.066666762
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson_tokyo",
      "startTime": 97.8333334286
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "……お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you for your hard work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4666703223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと練習してたんですか？\n少し休憩したらどうですか、これスポーツドリンクです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Have you been practicing all this time?\nHow about taking a break? Here‚ have a sports drink.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1666698137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… thank you very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7333364803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、先日の祭典なんですけど\n俺としては、決して悪い話じゃないと思うんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ about the festival the other day…\nFrom my perspective‚ it's not necessarily a bad thing‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.1999990779,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9133.333746600001,
          "startTime": 123.3333328245
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "その話は先日、お断りしたはずです\n失礼します、ロッカーから資料を取って来るので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I declined that offer the other day.\nIf you'll excuse me‚ I have to get some materials from my locker.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.2333324113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ちょっ……\nはぁ……ろくに話も聞いてもらえないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ wait a…\nSigh… Can't even get a proper conversation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4666723567,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6266.661580499999,
          "startTime": 133.7333339372
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6266.661580499999,
          "startTime": 133.7333339372
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 133.4833339372
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 133.4833339372
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "……あら、{user}さん\nこんな所で会うなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ {user}-san.\nMeeting you in a place like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.7666520117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "こんな所って、事務所はすぐそこじゃないですか\nたまには息抜きに一杯やるのもいいかと思いまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Meeting in a place like this‚ huh? But isn't the office right nearby?\nI thought it might be nice to take a break and have a drink sometimes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.6999924658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 146.566673374
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（本当は、mihoさんが居酒屋に入ったのを見て）\n（追いかけて来たんだけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Actually‚ I saw miho-san going into the pub and）\n（I followed her in.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.866673374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 152.0000067073
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "私も息抜きです\n普段、お酒はあまり飲まないようにしてるんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm taking a break too.\nI usually try not to drink much‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.1333400407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
